26#include "archive_platform.h"
27__FBSDID("$FreeBSD: head/lib/libarchive/archive_entry_copy_stat.c 189466 2009-03-07 00:52:02Z kientzle $");
28
29#ifdef HAVE_SYS_STAT_H
30#include <sys/stat.h>
31#endif
32
33#include "archive.h"
34#include "archive_entry.h"
35
36void
37archive_entry_copy_stat(struct archive_entry *entry, const struct stat *st)
38{
39#if HAVE_STRUCT_STAT_ST_MTIMESPEC_TV_NSEC
40 archive_entry_set_atime(entry, st->st_atime, st->st_atimespec.tv_nsec);
41 archive_entry_set_ctime(entry, st->st_ctime, st->st_ctimespec.tv_nsec);
42 archive_entry_set_mtime(entry, st->st_mtime, st->st_mtimespec.tv_nsec);
43#elif HAVE_STRUCT_STAT_ST_MTIM_TV_NSEC
44 archive_entry_set_atime(entry, st->st_atime, st->st_atim.tv_nsec);
45 archive_entry_set_ctime(entry, st->st_ctime, st->st_ctim.tv_nsec);
46 archive_entry_set_mtime(entry, st->st_mtime, st->st_mtim.tv_nsec);
47#elif HAVE_STRUCT_STAT_ST_MTIME_NSEC
48 archive_entry_set_atime(entry, st->st_atime, st->st_atime_nsec);
49 archive_entry_set_ctime(entry, st->st_ctime, st->st_ctime_nsec);
50 archive_entry_set_mtime(entry, st->st_mtime, st->st_mtime_nsec);
51#elif HAVE_STRUCT_STAT_ST_MTIME_N
52 archive_entry_set_atime(entry, st->st_atime, st->st_atime_n);
53 archive_entry_set_ctime(entry, st->st_ctime, st->st_ctime_n);
54 archive_entry_set_mtime(entry, st->st_mtime, st->st_mtime_n);
55#elif HAVE_STRUCT_STAT_ST_UMTIME
56 archive_entry_set_atime(entry, st->st_atime, st->st_uatime * 1000);
57 archive_entry_set_ctime(entry, st->st_ctime, st->st_uctime * 1000);
58 archive_entry_set_mtime(entry, st->st_mtime, st->st_umtime * 1000);
59#elif HAVE_STRUCT_STAT_ST_MTIME_USEC
60 archive_entry_set_atime(entry, st->st_atime, st->st_atime_usec * 1000);
61 archive_entry_set_ctime(entry, st->st_ctime, st->st_ctime_usec * 1000);
62 archive_entry_set_mtime(entry, st->st_mtime, st->st_mtime_usec * 1000);
63#else
64 archive_entry_set_atime(entry, st->st_atime, 0);
65 archive_entry_set_ctime(entry, st->st_ctime, 0);
66 archive_entry_set_mtime(entry, st->st_mtime, 0);
67#endif
68#if HAVE_STRUCT_STAT_ST_BIRTHTIMESPEC_TV_NSEC
69 archive_entry_set_birthtime(entry, st->st_birthtime, st->st_birthtimespec.tv_nsec);
70#elif HAVE_STRUCT_STAT_ST_BIRTHTIME
71 archive_entry_set_birthtime(entry, st->st_birthtime, 0);
72#else
73 archive_entry_unset_birthtime(entry);
74#endif
75 archive_entry_set_dev(entry, st->st_dev);
76 archive_entry_set_gid(entry, st->st_gid);
77 archive_entry_set_uid(entry, st->st_uid);
78 archive_entry_set_ino(entry, st->st_ino);
79 archive_entry_set_nlink(entry, st->st_nlink);
80 archive_entry_set_rdev(entry, st->st_rdev);
81 archive_entry_set_size(entry, st->st_size);
82 archive_entry_set_mode(entry, st->st_mode);
83}
